Class FlyCapture2_C.fc2Property

  • java.lang.Object

    FlyCapture2_C

    public static class FlyCapture2_C.fc2Property
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    A specific camera property. \n For example, to set the gain to 12dB, set the following values: - \a type - \c GAIN - \a absControl - \c true - \a onePush - \c false - \a onOff - \c true - \a autoManualMode - \c false - \a absValue - \c 12.0
